response.overview: ELVIS PRESLEY - "LAST CONCERT" Market Square Arena, INDIANAPOLIS 26/06/1977  This is Elvis Presley Final Performance Filmed During his last Concert In Indianapolis on 26/06/1977.Chapter 1) The Concert - 52 minutes of Elvis Final performance. Captured 8mm cameras by fans now digitally enhanced and pieced together to bring this ultimate historic event. Chapter 2) Elvis at Indianapolis Airport- see Elvis descend from his private jet (the Lisa Marie) to accept awards from RCA records and Todd Slaughter his arrival on 26/6/77. (silent footage) Chapter 3) Bonus 8mm Footage - Elvis Final stage entrance from an alternative camera angle. (silent footage) Chapter 4) A Day in Pictures - Photo album of June 26, 1977
response.title: Elvis Presley: Final Performance
